sentence: Mark Vadon, Director at Home Depot ( HD ) bought 15,000 shares of the company's common stock on November 29.
The shares were purchased at $129.87 for a total of $1,948,050.00.
IK-> The technicals for HD ($129.95 up $0.12) are neutral with a neutral trend.
Support has been around $124.40 and the stock resistance around $131.57.
Look at the February 110/115 bull-put spread for a 31-cent credit.
That's a 6.6% return and the stock has to fall 11.5% to cause a problem.
